high_descs: Turn left and walk halfway across the room until you are even with the stove then turn right and walk to the stove so you are facing the front of it.
Pick up the frying pan on the bottom left burner.
Turn left and walk to the fridge and face it.
Open the fridge and place the frying pan on the top shelf to the right and close the door letting it chill for a while before retrieving it and closing the door.
Position yourself back in front of the stove where you were before.
Place the frying pan back on the stove but on the top left burner this time.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled frying pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, and hang right to face the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front left burner.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the pan on the right shelf. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the pan back out.
Turn right and take a few steps. Face the stove.
Place the pan on the back left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on a stove.

high_descs: Turn left and walk ahead, veering right to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Take a few steps left.
Place the pan in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment and take the pan back out.
Take a few steps back until you're facing the stove again.
Place the pan on the back left burner on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled plate on a stove.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight. Halfway turn right and go to the stove.
Pick up the frying pan on the stove.
Turn left, walk straight making a right to face the fridge.
Put the frying pan on the shelf in the fridge and shut the door. After a few seconds take the pan back out.
Turn around to take a step towards the table and turn left. Walk to the stove and turn left to face it.
Place the frying pan on the back burner.
anns.task_desc: To place the pan in the fridge to go back on the stove top.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the pan inside then close the door. Wait a few seconds then open the door and take the pan out. Close the door.
Walk back over to the stove.
Put the pan onto the back of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled down pan onto the back of the stove.

high_descs: move left towards the gas
pick up the pan from the gas
move left towards the fridge
place the pan in the fridge to cool and then take it out
turn right and head for the gas
place the pan on the gas
anns.task_desc: place a cold pan on the gas
